hisat_caller identifies the pairs of fastq files which belong together and passes them to hisat_execute
hisat_execute does the actual hisat_call
samtool_sorter Presorts the files so that they can then be merged by samtool_merger 

Splitting the code this much is admittedly highly unnnessary but those were the first scripts written in this project and going back to clean them
up and combine them wasn't really a priority given the other more urgent issues with the project
